name: Ext_R5_ObservationDefinition_experimental
title: Cross-version Extension for R5.ObservationDefinition.experimental for use in FHIR R4B
description: This cross-version extension represents ObservationDefinition.experimental from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/ObservationDefinition|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4B.

element.short: If for testing purposes, not real usage
element.definition: A flag to indicate that this ObservationDefinition is authored for testing purposes (or education/evaluation/marketing), and is not intended to be used for genuine usage.
element.comment: `ObservationDefinition.experimental` has no related element in R4B:ObservationDefinition
